Package edu.colorado.cires.cmg.hullgen

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GeometryProcessor
    Processes geometries and coordinates with Uber's H3 library
    Hull
    Processes H3 ids into Geometry containing hulls
    InputFileProcessor
    Generates hull from input File
    OutputFileReader
    Reads Geometry from input File
    OutputFileWriter
    Writes Geometry to output File
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseGeometryProcessor
    Base implementation of GeometryProcessor
    BaseHull
    Base implementation of Hull
    BufferedHull
    Implementation of BaseHull which generates and merges hulls according to the size of its point buffer
    CompleteGeometryProcessor
    Implementation of BaseGeometryProcessor which processes H3 ids without simplification
    CompleteHull
    Implementation of BaseHull which processes all H3 ids at once
    CSVProcessor
    Implementation of InputFileProcessor which computes hulls from CSV coordinates (longitude/latitude column order)
    GeoJSONReader
    Reads Geometry from GeoJSON format
    GeoJSONWriter
    Writes from input Geometry to output GeoJson File
    GeoTiffMetadata
    Information related to a GeoTIFF image
    GeoTiffProcessor
    Implementation of InputFileProcessor which computes hulls from a GeoTiff image
    GeoTiffTags
    TIFF tag IDs related to GeoTIFF images
    HullGenerator
    Computes hull from input file and writes to output file
    InvertCoordinateFilter
    Inverts coordinates belonging to a Geometry
    MultiFileHullMerger
    Merges Geometry from multiple files
    SimplifyingGeometryProcessor
    Implementation of BaseGeometryProcessor which simplifies output geometry
    WktReader
    Reads Geometry from WKT format
    WktWriter
    Writes from input Geometry to output WKT File
